'''芬蘭國家劇院'''（{{lang-fi|Suomen Kansallisteatteri}}）是[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]的國家[[劇院|劇院]]，位於芬蘭首都[[赫爾辛基|赫爾辛基]]的[[赫尔辛基铁路广场|铁路广场]]。芬蘭國家劇院成立於1872年，當時位於[[波里|波里]]，是芬蘭歷史最久的一家芬蘭語專業劇院。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.kansallisteatteri.fi/briefly-in-english/|title = Briefly in english|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Kansallisteatteri|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204815/http://www.kansallisteatteri.fi/briefly-in-english/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://helsinkithisweek.com/finnish-national-theatre|title = Finnish National Theatre|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Helsinki This Week|archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305155959/http://helsinkithisweek.com/finnish-national-theatre|dead-url = no}}</ref>在1902年之前，名為'''芬蘭劇院'''，之後迁址至赫尔辛基，改名為芬蘭國家劇院。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.building.am/page.php?id=553|title = Finnish National Theatre, Helsinki, Finland|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Building.am|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304163550/http://www.building.am/page.php?id=553|dead-url = no}}</ref>

